<span id="freeTextContainer4402437580812571748">This book had my interest for about 100 pages. What is attractive about obscene amounts of money? The characters are flat and Grisham portrays the women as objects.<br/><br/>The second reading showed the stereotype grisham uses to portray lawyers. It is not flattering and probably promulgates the negative view.</span>

          </span>
